data.description: Check out this adorable, updated QUAD level, in an awesome location in Munster! On the main floor you'll love the open concept and large amount of natural light! The spacious kitchen has been updated and has lots of cabinet space! There is also ample space for a dining table and additional seating. The upper level features 3 nice sized bedrooms! The main bedroom has its own bath, double closet, and plenty of room for all of your furniture! The first lower level is a second living space as well as a bonus space for an additional bedroom, an office, a playroom, or whatever you need it to be! The lowest level (basement) is great for all of your storage or could be finished one day for an additional bonus space! The fenced in yard is great for entertaining and features a patio ready for grilling season! This home is close to all of the wonderful things Munster has to offer, shops, restaurants, parks, a bike path, dog park, golf courses, and SO much more! You do not want to miss this one!
